Articles.Content: Hi Baladain, that log only tells us that you ran out of addressable memory, your KSP.log and output_log can tell us more, please see the support stickies for more info on these

Hi Baladain, that log only tells us that you ran out of addressable memory, your KSP.log and output_log can tell us more, please see the support stickies for more info on these

That's what I thought it said. Thank you for the confirmation. Now comes the mystery of figuring out why 5GB of my system ram isn't being reported by windows
